---
// hospitality-food-service.astro - Hospitality & Food Service B2B Detail Page
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Resort & Food Service Supply | Sosun Fihaara"
  description="High-quality food service, beverage, and dairy supply lines for resorts, cafes, and restaurants across the Maldives."
>
  <main class="bg-[#F6F2E8] py-20 min-h-screen pt-28">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-5">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <div class="mb-6 font-body text-xs text-[#566159] uppercase tracking-wider">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#00663B] no-underline">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
        <a href="/distribution" class="hover:text-[#00663B] no-underline">Distribution</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
        <span class="text-[#18231D]">Hospitality &amp; Food Service</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-[#D8D4C9] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm mb-12">
        <div class="aspect-[16/6] w-full bg-[#EAE6DC] overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/hospitality_supply.png" alt="Resort culinary team plating fine dining meals in professional kitchen" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-[#DDEBE2] text-[#00663B] px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            B2B Services
          </span>

          <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-[#18231D] leading-tight mt-4 mb-6" style="font-size: var(--type-h2);">
            Hospitality &amp; Food Service Supply
          </h1>

          <div class="prose font-body text-base text-[#18231D] leading-relaxed max-w-none mb-8">
            <p class="mb-4">
              Providing culinary staples and premium ingredients to the resort kitchens, hotels, cafés, and restaurants of the Maldives. We understand that premium food service requires absolute reliability, long shelf lives, and strict cold-chain compliance.
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#18231D] mt-6 mb-3">Resort Supply Capabilities</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-6 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <li><strong>High-Quality Dairy Imports:</strong> Exclusively distributing European milk, creams, yogurts, and butter (like Pascual) kept in active cold storage.</li>
              <li><strong>Resort Food Service Packaging:</strong> Catering-size packages, bulk cooking oils, flour, sugar, and food service pantry staples.</li>
              <li><strong>Doha/Port-to-Resort Transit:</strong> Coordination with resort supply dhonis, charter transport, and cold-freight agents.</li>
              <li><strong>F&B Quote Desk:</strong> Quick, clear invoices, volume discount rates, and detailed packing lists.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- B2B CTA band inside page -->
          <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[#D8D4C9]/40 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 bg-[#DDEBE2]/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-[#083C2B] mb-1">Talk to our Sales Team</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-xs text-[#566159] leading-relaxed">
                Connect with our resort trade desk to establish a supply account.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 w-full md:w-auto shrink-0 justify-center">
              <a href="/request-quote" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
              <a href="/products" class="btn-secondary">Explore Products</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-surface) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.16s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-green-dark);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-green) !important;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-green);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.16s ease, color 0.16s ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-surface) !important;
  }
</style>
